Class Applicant

Object
User
Applicant
Direct Known Subclasses:
HDBOfficer
public class Applicant extends User
Represents an applicant for BTO housing projects. Applicants can apply for projects, view their applications, and book flats.
Since:
2025-03-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
SC2002 G Team
